00:00:06.482 --> 00:00:08.848
<i>- He eats three times a day.</i>

00:00:10.119 --> 00:00:12.553
<i>If he looks starved, feed him again.</i>

00:00:14.290 --> 00:00:17.157
<i>Now, of course, all of this food</i>
<i>is gonna have to go somewhere...</i>

00:00:17.226 --> 00:00:21.162
