00:00:21.230 --> 00:00:24.028
<i>Don't worry about the color.</i>
<i>He likes mangoes.</i>

00:00:24.100 --> 00:00:26.330
<i>Marley is not allowed</i>
<i>to drink out of the toilet...</i>

00:00:26.402 --> 00:00:28.836
<i>so be sure to keep the lid closed...</i>

00:00:28.905 --> 00:00:30.839
<i>- and the brick on the lid.</i>

00:00:30.907 --> 00:00:32.841
<i>You know, actually,</i>
<i>you might want...</i>

00:00:32.909 --> 00:00:34.843
