<i>shut in general.</i>

00:00:34.911 --> 00:00:37.573
<i>Like most dogs, Marley</i>
<i>needs a lot of exercise...</i>

00:00:37.647 --> 00:00:42.584
<i>so try to take him for a walk or a run</i>
<i>every morning and every evening.</i>

00:00:42.652 --> 00:00:44.950
Marley, let go!

00:00:45.021 --> 00:00:47.421
Let go. Let go. Let go.
Aaah! Marley, no!

00:00:47.490 --> 00:00:50.857
<i>And be sure to lock the doors</i>
<i>and windows before you go to sleep.</i>

00:00:50.927 --> 00:00:52.292
Shoo! Shoo!

00:00:52.362 --> 00:00:54.853
<i>But don't worry.</i>
<i>Marley is an excellent watchdog.</i>

00:00:56.933 --> 00:00:59.925
<i>You can rest easy at night</i>
<i>knowing he's on the job.</i>

00:01:00.002 --> 00:01:02.266
<i>Thunderstorms are his weak point.</i>

00:01:02.338 --> 00:01:04.966
