<i>if you think a storm is arriving.</i>

00:01:05.041 --> 00:01:08.568
Okay. Here you go. Marley.
Marley, come back here.

00:01:08.644 --> 00:01:12.080
<i>He doesn't like them, so push them</i>
<i>down his throat as far as they go.</i>

00:01:12.148 --> 00:01:15.379
Welcome. Welcome.
I'm Mrs. Butterly.

00:01:15.451 --> 00:01:19.911
<i>Now finally, we do not allow Marley</i>
<i>to get up on any piece of furniture...</i>

00:01:19.989 --> 00:01:22.116
<i>chew on anything except his toys.</i>

00:01:23.826 --> 00:01:27.592
<i>Other than that, enjoy him.</i>
<i>Love, Jenny and John.</i>

